\f4\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 24\'a0
\f5\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93The God who made the world and everything in it\'a0is the Lord of heaven and earth\'a0and does not live in temples built by human hands.\'a0
\f4\b\fs18 \super 25\'a0
